reviewText:
A fantastic game with a great concept and an incledible combination of action, story and touching a polemical topic: sustainable thinking, showing the two sides of the coin.

+Marvelous and surprising story;
+Good combination of scenarios and soundtrack;
+Challenging puzzles and funny achievments.

-The player doesn't have the chance to understant every character;

